<!-- ======== CAROUSEL =========-->

<div class="carousel fade-carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="4000" id="bs-carousel">

    <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="item slides active">
            <div class="slide-1"></div>
            <div class="hero">
                <hgroup>
                    <h1 class="white">Lodging</h1>
                    <h3 class="white">Enjoy your stay</h3>
                    <h5 class="white">Click on Learn more, for more information</h5>
                </hgroup>
                <form style="display: inline" action="http://52.29.34.251/Home/Notice" method="get">
                    <button class="btn btn-hero btn-lg" role="button">Learn more</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ========= END OF CAROUSEL ========== -->

<div class="sadrzaj">
    <h3>@ViewBag.Header</h3>
    <hr />
    <h4>Idea for showing place to stay, goes like this, text below is just an example:</h4>
    <p>
        Few sentences about place of interest no more than, three or four, if the place is for example hotel, include things like:
        <ul>
            <li>How many rooms does it have?</li>
            <li>How much money does it cost to rent a room for a night, two, three?</li>
            <li>Do they serve breakfast, lunch, dinner?</li>
            <li>Include the amount of seats, include the menu, do they have specials?</li>
            <li>Include working hours, does it have WIFI etc.</li>
            <li>Include few pictures, or just one, then when users click on Learn more button, take them to a new page with more detailed information about the place.</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <form style="display: inline" action="http://52.29.34.251/Home/Notice" method="get">
        <button class="btn btn-hero btn-lg" role="button">Learn more</button>
    </form>
</div>
